                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="hourlySetup" ng-show="hourlyEnabled">
                            <span> starting between </span>
                            <div class="btn-group" uib-dropdown>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle FS-Button" uib-dropdown-toggle>
                                    {{generateHourSpanString(schedule.hourly.start.hour)}}
                                    <span class="caret"></span>
                                </button>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu" uib-dropdown-menu role="menu">
                                    <li ng-repeat="hour in schedule.constants.hours"><a href="#" ng-click="selectHourlyStartHour(hour)">{{generateHourSpanString(hour)}}</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="btn-group" uib-dropdown>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle FS-Button" uib-dropdown-toggle>
                                    {{schedule.hourly.start.meridian}}
                                    <span class="caret"></span>
                                </button>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu" uib-dropdown-menu role="menu">
                                    <li ng-repeat="meridian in schedule.constants.meridian"><a href="#" ng-click="selectHourlyStartMeridian(meridian)">{{meridian}}</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <span> and ending at </span>
                            <div class="btn-group" uib-dropdown>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle FS-Button" uib-dropdown-toggle>
                                    {{generateHourString(schedule.hourly.end.hour)}}
                                    <span class="caret"></span>
                                </button>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu" uib-dropdown-menu role="menu">
                                    <li ng-repeat="hour in schedule.constants.hours"><a href="#" ng-click="selectHourlyEndHour(hour)">{{generateHourString(hour)}}</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="btn-group" uib-dropdown>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle FS-Button" uib-dropdown-toggle>
                                    {{schedule.hourly.end.meridian}}
                                    <span class="caret"></span>
                                </button>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu" uib-dropdown-menu role="menu">
                                    <li ng-repeat="meridian in schedule.constants.meridian"><a href="#" ng-click="selectHourlyEndMeridian(meridian)">{{meridian}}</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <span ng-show="scheduleSpansDay()" class="hourlyScheduleSuffix">
                                the next day
                            </span>
                        </div>

                        <div ng-hide="manualEnabled">
                            <div class="scheduleOption" ng-show="isSyncErrorNotificationsEnabled()">
                                <input type="checkbox" ng-model="tableInfo.notifyOnFailure" value="true">
                                <div class="scheduleOptionInputLabel">
                                    Email me if there's a problem refreshing my table<br />
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>

</script>

<script type="text/javascript" id="navResourcesEventingJs">
    window.QB = window.QB || {};
    window.QB.Nav = window.QB.Nav || {};

    QB.Nav.Eventing = {
        events: {
            NAV_CONNECTED_TABLE_OPEN_CREATE_DIALOG: 'nav-connected-table-open-create-dialog',
            NAV_NEW_SCRATCH_TABLE_OPEN_CREATE_DIALOG: 'nav-new-scratch-table-open-create-dialog',
            NAV_TEST_AS_ROLE: 'nav-test-as-role',
            NAV_TEST_AS_USER: 'nav-test-as-user',
            NAV_TEST_AS_ERROR: 'nav-test-as-error',
        }
    }

    const isTestingAsRole = '';
    const isTestingAsUser = '';

    QB.Nav.initTestAsEvents = function () {
        if (!window.gPubSub) {
            console.log("PubSub has not been loaded. Make sure Huey is running and QbGlobalVars has been initialized before calling this function");
            return;
        }

        const restyledBannerSwitchesOn = QB.FeatureSwitchMgr.isSwitchOn('Switch_RemixLegacyUserMenuRestyled') && QB.FeatureSwitchMgr.isSwitchOn('Switch_RestyledTestAsBanners');

        if (restyledBannerSwitchesOn && isTestingAsRole) {
            gPubSub.publish(QB.Nav.Eventing.events.NAV_TEST_AS_ROLE, { data: isTestingAsRole });
        }
        if (restyledBannerSwitchesOn && isTestingAsUser) {
            gPubSub.publish(QB.Nav.Eventing.events.NAV_TEST_AS_USER, { data: isTestingAsUser });
        }
    }

    QB.Nav.initNewTableEvents = function () {
        if (!window.gPubSub) {
            console.log("PubSub has not been loaded. Make sure Huey is running and QbGlobalVars has been initialized before calling this function");
            return;
        }

        gPubSub.subscribe(QB.Nav.Eventing.events.NAV_CONNECTED_TABLE_OPEN_CREATE_DIALOG, function (topic, payload) {
            if (!document.getElementById('nav-btnNewReplicatedTable')) {
                const tempButton = document.createElement('button');
                tempButton.setAttribute('qb-new-connected-table', '');
                tempButton.setAttribute('id', 'nav-btnNewReplicatedTable');
                tempButton.style.display = 'none';
                document.body.appendChild(tempButton);
            }

            const navBtnNewReplicatedTable = document.getElementById('nav-btnNewReplicatedTable');

            require(["connect.wizardDialog", "connect.logout"],
                function () {
                    if (!navBtnNewReplicatedTable.classList.contains('ng-scope')) {
                        angular.bootstrap(navBtnNewReplicatedTable, ["qb.connect.wizardDialog", "qb.connect.logout"]);
                    }
                    navBtnNewReplicatedTable.click();
                }
            );
        });

        gPubSub.subscribe(QB.Nav.Eventing.events.NAV_NEW_SCRATCH_TABLE_OPEN_CREATE_DIALOG, function (topic, payload) {
            requireHueyFeature(['ui-smart-builder'], function (SmartBuilder) {
                SmartBuilder.runSetup.setup({ showDialog: true, isRemix: true });
            }, function (error) {
                Log.error('There was likely a network problem loading smart-builder feature. Error Message: ' + error);
            });
        });
    }
</script>

        function loadTestAsFuncionality() {
            //if element exists (test as is available, then bootsrap)
            var testAsElement = $("#testAs");
            if (testAsElement.length > 0) {
                require(["angular", "testAs"], function (angular) {
                    var module = angular.module("qb.test.as");
                    module.constant("Roles", [{"first":"Viewer","luid":10,"type":"role"},{"first":"Administrator","luid":12,"type":"role"},{"first":"Admin - Read Only","luid":13,"type":"role"},{"first":"Exchange Consumer Role 2","luid":33,"type":"role"}]);
                    module.constant("Users", []);
                    //check if already boostrapped
                    if (!testAsElement.injector()) {
                        angular.bootstrap(testAsElement, ["qb.test.as"]);
                    }
                });
            }

            loadServiceAccountMenu();
        }

    <script type="text/ng-template" id="inlineUserPicker/iup-picker.html" class="Selectable" tabindex="0">

moreInfo.position.end.column;\n\n\t    var line = session.doc.getAllLines()[position.row];\n\t    var sortByKey = \"\";\n\n\t    if(line){\n\t        sortByKey = cp\u003e=0 ?\n                 line.substring(position.column, cp).toLowerCase() :\n                 line.substring(position.column).toLowerCase();\n\t    }\n\n\t    var suggestedList = [];\n\t    //If the offending symbol starts with $ then populate declarations first.\n\t    if(sortByKey.indexOf('$') == 0 || word == '$')\n\t        suggestedList = renderDeclarationsToTokenHelper(aceEditor, moreInfo, sortByKey).concat(renderFieldsToTokenHelper(aceEditor, fields, moreInfo, sortByKey));\n\t    else\n\t        suggestedList = renderFieldsToTokenHelper(aceEditor, fields, moreInfo, sortByKey).concat(renderDeclarationsToTokenHelper(aceEditor, moreInfo, sortByKey));\n\n\t    return suggestedList;\n\t}\n\n\tfunction renderQBTypesToTokenHelper(aceEditor, offendingTokenHelper, info) {\n\t    var qbTypes =  [\"WorkDate\", \"UserList\", \"User\", \"TimeOfDay\", \"Text\", \"Number\", \"Duration\", \"DateTime\", \"Date\", \"Bool\", \"TextList\"];\n\t    var ctn = containsKey = [], others = [];\n\t    for (var i = 0; i \u003c tokenHelperList.length; i++)\n\t    {\n\t        if (tokenHelperList[i].name.toLowerCase().indexOf(sortByKey) == 0)\n\t        {\n\t            first.push(tokenHelperList[i]);\n\t        } \n\t        else if (tokenHelperList[i].name.toLowerCase().indexOf(sortByKey) \u003e 0)\n\t        {\n\t            containsKey.push(tokenHelperList[i]);\n\t        } \n\t        else\n\t        {\n\t            others.push(tokenHelperList[i]);\n\t        }\n\t    }\n\t    return first.concat(containsKey).concat(others);\n\t}\n\n\tfunction getFieldInfo(formulaHelperId) {\n\t    var fields =[];\n\t    $('#'+ formulaHelperId +' option:not(disabled)').each(function(i, opt) {\n\t        var fType = $(opt).data('field-type');\n\t        if(fType) {\n\t            if(fType == 'Record ID#') fType = 'Numeric';\n\t            if(fType == 'URL' || fType == 'iCalendar' || fType == 'Predecessor' || fType == 'Email' \n                    || fType == 'Phone Number' || fType =='Address' || fType == 'vCard' || fType == 'File Attachment') fType = 'Text';\n\t            //Do not use jquery .text() or .val() as its changing the encoding and comparision is failing at parser leve;\n\t            var fName = $(opt)[0].value;\n\t            if (fName.substring(0, 1)  == \"[\" \u0026\u0026 fName.substring(fName.length, fName.length - 1) == \"]\") {\n\t                fName = fName.substring(1, fName.length - 1);\n\t            }\n\t            fields.push({ name: fName, type: fType, value: $(opt).attr('value') });\n\t        }\n\t    });\n\t    return fields;\n\t}\n\n\tfunction clearMarkers(aceSession) {\n\t    var keys = Object.keys(aceSession.$backMarkers);\n\n\t    for (var index = 0; index \u003c keys.length; index++) {\n\t        var marker = aceSession.$backMarkers[keys[index]];\n\t        if (!marker.range \u0026\u0026 typeof marker.update == 'function') {\n\t            aceSession.removeMarker(marker.id);\n\t        }\n\t    }\n\t}\n\n\tfunction getTypeNameforSuggestionLink(expectedType) {\n\t    var returnVal = { name: 'All', value:'All' };\n\t    switch (expectedType.toLowerCase()) {\n\t        case 'bool': \n\t            break;\n\t        case 'datetime': break;\n\t        case 'duration':\n\t            returnVal = { name: 'Duration', value:'Durations' };\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'numeric': \n\t            returnVal = { name: 'Numeric', value:'Numbers' };\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'text':\n\t            returnVal = { name: 'Text', value:'Text' };\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'userlist': \n\t        case 'user': \n\t            returnVal = { name: 'Special', value:'Special' };\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'date': \n\t            returnVal = { name: 'Date', value:'Dates' };\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'timeofday': \n\t            returnVal = { name: 'TimeOfDay', value:'TimeOfDay' };\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'workdate':\n\t            returnVal = { name: 'Work Date', value:'WorkDates' };\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'textlist':\n\t            returnVal = { name: 'Multi-select Text', value:'TextList' };\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'type': \n\t            returnVal = { name: 'type', value:'All' };\n\t            break;\n\t        default: break;\n\t    }\n\t    return returnVal;\n\t}\n\n\tfunction onSuggestedLinkClick(ele) {\n\t    var editorName = $(ele).data('target-editor');\n\t    var editor = $('#' + editorName + '_aceEditor');\n\t    if(editor.length == 0) return;\n\n\t    var aceEditor = ace.edit(editor[0]);\n\t    var session = aceEditor.getSession();\n\n        //Set the active editor to current formula builder\n\t    SetFieldTarget(aceEditor, $(ele).data('formula-helper-container'));\n\n\t    var moreInfo = typeof session.getAdditionalInfo == 'function' ? session.getAdditionalInfo() : null;\n\t    if(!moreInfo) return;\n\n\t    if(!moreInfo.expectedTypes || moreInfo.expectedTypes.length == 0) return; \n\n\t    replaceOffendingToken = true;\n\t    var typeName = getTypeNameforSuggestionLink(moreInfo.expectedTypes[0]);\n\t    var filterBy = $('#formulaFunctions [name=filterBy]');\n\t    filterBy.val(typeName.value);\n\t    RefreshFormulaInfoByCategory(filterBy[0]);\n\t    OpenFormulaFunctHelper();\n\n\t    return false;\n\t}\n\t// Print after variable to match with the QB field types\n\tfunction declarationTypeToQBType(typeName) {\n\t    switch (typeName) {\n\t        case 'number': return 'Numeric';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'datetime': return 'Date / Time';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'userlist': return 'List - User';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'date': return 'Date';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'duration': return 'Duration';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'timeofday': return 'Time Of Day';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'user': return 'User';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'text': return 'Text';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'bool': return 'Boolean';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'workdate': return 'Work Date';\n\t            break;\n\t        case 'textlist': return 'Multi-select Text';\n\t            break;\n\t        default: return typeName;\n\t    }\n\t}\n\n\tfunction renderDeclarationsToTokenHelper(editor, info, sortByKey) {\n\t    var expectedTypes = info.expectedTypes;\n\t    var filteredDeclarations = _.sortBy(_.filter(info.declarations, function(dec){\n\t        return _.find(expectedTypes, function(b){\n\t            return b.toLowerCase() === dec.type.toLowerCase()\n                    \u0026\u0026 dec.position.line \u003c= info.position.start.row+1;\n\t        });\n\t    }), function (i) { return i.name.trim().toLowerCase(); });\n\n\t    var offendingTokenHelper = editor.getSession().offendingTokenHelper;\n\n\t    //First populate the variables which start with the offending token.\n\t    if(sortByKey.indexOf('$')==0)\n\t    {\n\t    sortByKey = sortByKey.split('$').length\u003e1 ? sortByKey.split('$')[1] : sortByKey;\n\t    filteredDeclarations = sortTokenHelper(filteredDeclarations, sortByKey);\n\t   }\n\n\t     var decName = dec.name;\n                    var position = info.position;\n                    if(editor.session.getTextRange(editor.session.getWordRange(position.start.row, position.start.column)) == \"$\"){\n                        position.start.column = position.start.column - 1; \n                    }\n                    replaceTextInFormulaBuilder(editor, position, \"$\" + dec.name); \n                }).html('$'+dec.name + ' - ' + declarationTypeToQBType(dec.type)));\n\t    });\n\n\t    return filteredDeclarations;\n\t}\n\n\tfunction renderFieldsToTokenHelper(editor, fields, info, sortByKey) {\n\t    var expectedTypes = info.expectedTypes;\n\t    var filteredFields = _.sortBy(_.filter(fields, function(field){\n\t        return _.find(expectedTypes, function(b){\n\t            var bLower = b.toLowerCase();\n\t            if(bLower == 'number') b = 'numeric'; //In some cases parser returns number\n\t            else if(bLower == 'datetime') b = 'date / time';\n\t            else if(bLower == 'userlist') b = 'list - user';\n\t            else if(bLower == 'textlist') b = 'multi-select text';\n\t            else if(bLower == 'workdate') b = 'Work Date';\n\t            else if(bLower == 'bool') b = 'Checkbox';\n\t            else if(bLower == 'timeofday') b = 'Time of Day';\n\t            return bLower === field.type.toLowerCase();\n\t        });\n\t    }), function (i) { return i.name.trim().toLowerCase(); });\n\t   var offendingTokenHelper = editor.getSession().offendingTokenHelper;\n\n\t    //First populate the fields which start with the offending token.\n\t   if(sortByKey.indexOf('$')!=0)\n\t   {\n\t       //Ignore the ']' character at the end of field name while sorting\n\t       if(sortByKey.indexOf(']')==sortByKey.length-1){\n\t           sortByKey = sortByKey.slice(']', sortByKey.length-1);\n\t       }\n\n\t       //Ignore the '[' character at the end of field name while sorting\n\t       if(sortByKey.indexOf('[')==0){\n\t           sortByKey = sortByKey.split('[')[1];\n\t       }\n\t       filteredFields = sortTokenHelper(filteredFields, sortByKey);\n\t   }\n\n\t replaceTextInFormulaBuilder(editor, info.position, field.value);\n                }).text(field.value + ' - ' + field.type));\n\t    });\n\n\t    return filteredFields;\n\t}\n\t\n    var declarationTypes = ['bool', 'number', 'text', 'date', 'datetime', 'duration', 'timeofday', 'workdate', 'user', 'userlist', 'textlist'];\n\tfunction configAutoComplete(fields, aceEditor) {\n\t    var fieldFormulaCompleter = {\n\t        getCompletions: function(editor, session, pos, prefix, callback) {\n\t            var word = session.getTextRange(session.getWordRange(pos.row, pos.column));\n\t            var worList = [];\n\t            $(fields).each(function(i, f) {\n\t                if(f.value == \"Select a function...\") return;\n                    //If any duplicate names exists in \u003e -1 ? 'AppVariable/Field - Text' : 'Field - ' + f.type, completer: this, type:'field' });\n\t            });\n\n \n\t            //Add all available functions\n\t            for (var func in gFuncMap) {\n\t                var f = gFuncMap[func];\n\t                worList.push({ name: f.name + f.args, value:  f.name + f.args, meta: f.category, completer: this, type:'function' });\n\t            }\n\n\t            //Add QB Types\n\t            declarationTypes.forEach(function(d) {\n\t                worList.push({ name: d, value:  d.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + d.slice(1), meta: d, completer: this, //QBMenu delays hiding menu for few milli seconds\n\t    //replacing text in editor causes re-rendering of the builder and QBMenu instance is lost\n\t    setTimeout(function() {\n\n            //Avoid value);\n\t        editor.focus();\n\t    }, 50);\n\t}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"formulaFunctions\"
